title: Snaps - Tennessee-Georgia elimination game? Will LSU topple Alabama? Clemson on upset alert vs ND
itunes:title: Snaps - Tennessee-Georgia elimination game? Will LSU topple Alabama? Clemson on upset alert vs ND
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert preview the biggest games from Week 10 of the college football season including Kirby Smart and the third ranked Georgia Bulldogs taking on Heisman favorite Hendon Hooker and the top ranked Tennessee Volunteers. How close to an elimination game is this for both SEC East schools? The guys also discuss Brian Kelly and LSU hosting Nick Saban's Alabama Crimson Tide, who are one loss away from likely missing the College Football Playoff for just the second time ever. Later, Aaron and T-Bob share their thoughts on other impactful Week 10 games including Clemson-Notre Dame, Texas Tech-TCU, and Texas-Kansas State. #Volume #ColinCowherd #Herd
